Key Match Events: Benin come from behind to beat Nigeria 2-1 for dia group C World Cup qualifying match.
Onyedika score for Nigeria na Chukwueze give am di pass.
Dossou na im score afta Bassey miss di ball for Benin equalise Nigeria goal.
Pre-Game Insights: Head-to-Head: Nigeria dey always dominate against Benin Republic afta dem win 13 of dia 16 games, wit two draws and one loss.
The Super Eagles win dia last three matches against Benin while di only victory by Benin na for 2017.
Post-Match Reflections: Di result mean say Nigeria dey fifth position wit four points for table, while Benin dey top group C wit seven points.
If di oda teams for di group win dia games Nigeria go dey bottom of di group.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Di Africa edition of di 2026 World Cup qualifiers go kontinu for almost two years.
